it.polimi.ingsw.common.reducedmodel

Packages that use it.polimi.ingsw.common.reducedmodel
Package
Description
it.polimi.ingsw.client
Classes that implement the client of the Masters of Renaissance game.
it.polimi.ingsw.client.cli.components
Classes that implement the graphical components of the command-line interface of the client of the Masters of Renaissance game.
it.polimi.ingsw.client.gui.components
Classes that implement the graphical components of the graphical user interface of the client of the Masters of Renaissance game.
it.polimi.ingsw.common.backend.model
Classes that implement the model of the server of the Masters of Renaissance game.
it.polimi.ingsw.common.backend.model.actiontokens
This package contains the implementation of the action tokens of the solo version of Masters of Renaissance.
it.polimi.ingsw.common.backend.model.cardrequirements
This package contains the implementation of the card requirements of Masters of Renaissance.
it.polimi.ingsw.common.backend.model.leadercards
This package contains the implementation of the leader cards of Masters of Renaissance.
it.polimi.ingsw.common.backend.model.resourcecontainers
This package contains the implementation of the resource containers of Masters of Renaissance.
it.polimi.ingsw.common.backend.model.resourcetransactions
This package contains the implementation of the resource transactions of Masters of Renaissance.
it.polimi.ingsw.common.backend.model.resourcetypes
This package contains the implementation of the resource types of Masters of Renaissance.
it.polimi.ingsw.common.events.mvevents
Classes that implement the events from the model to a view of the Masters of Renaissance game.
it.polimi.ingsw.common.events.mvevents.errors
Classes that implement the error events from the model to a view of the Masters of Renaissance game.
it.polimi.ingsw.common.events.vcevents
Classes that implement the events from a view to the controller of the Masters of Renaissance game.
it.polimi.ingsw.common.reducedmodel
Classes that implement the reduced model of the Masters of Renaissance game.
